Class Bend

  • Object
    • Bend

  • public class Bend
extends Object
    A bend in a line (e.g. in a mountain road). The extent of the bend has to be computed in some way.

      • getSymmetry

        public double getSymmetry()
        Compute a measure of bend symmetry. If D1 is the curvilinear length from bend start and bend summit and D2 the curvilinear length between bend end and bend summit, symmetry is Min(D1,D2)/Max(D1,D2).
        Returns:
        a value between 0 and 1.
